nav":{"en":"Buy","zh-CN":""},"v4.nav_menu.agriculture.solution.title":{"en":"Solutions","zh-CN":"解决方案"},"v4.nav_menu.automotive.solution.title":{"en":"Solutions","zh-CN":"解决方案"},"v4.nav_menu.education.solution.title":{"en":"Education","zh-CN":"教育应用"},"v4.nav_menu.enterprise.solution.title":{"en":"Solutions","zh-CN":"解决方案"},"v4.nav_menu.product.new.text":{"en":"New","zh-CN":"新品"},"v4.sample.main.title":{"en":"Sample Footage","zh-CN":"画质样片"},"v4.support.search":{"en":"Search","zh-CN":"查询"},"v4.support.search.placeholder":{"en":"Please enter keywords","zh-CN":"请输入您想了解的信息"},"v4.wm162.note1":{"en":"* Please check and strictly abide by local laws and regulations before flying.","zh-CN":"* 请在飞行前查询、确认并严格遵守当地法律法规。"},"v4.wm162.note10":{"en":"7. FocusTrack is not available while recording 4K/48fps, 4K/50fps, 4K/60fps, 2.7K/48fps, 2.7K/50fps, 2.7K/60fps, 1080p/48fps, 1080p/50fps, 1080p/60fps, and 1080p/120fps video.","zh-CN":"[6] 录制 4K/48fps、4K/50fps、4K/60fps、2.7K/48fps、2.7K/50fps、2.7K/60fps、1080p/48fps、1080p/50fps、1080p/60fps、1080p/120fps 视频时，焦点跟随功能不可用。"},"v4.wm162.note11":{"en":"8. Sold separately. Availability may vary.","zh-CN":"[7] 该配件需单独购买，请以实际发售时间为准。"},"v4.wm162.note12":{"en":"9. Requires the purchase of DJI Mini 3 Pro (DJI RC version).","zh-CN":"[8] 该配件需通过购买 DJI Mini 3 Pro 带屏遥控器版获得。"},"v4.wm162.note2":{"en":"** Tested with a production model DJI Mini 3 Pro in a controlled environment. Actual experience may vary depending on the environment, usage, and firmware version.","zh-CN":"** 本页面所列出的各项参数数值，均为量产版 DJI Mini 3 Pro 飞行器在受控测试环境下测得，在不同的外部环境、使用方式、固件版本下，结果或有不同程度的差异，请以实际体验为准。"},"v4.wm162.note3":{"en":"*** All videos and photos on this page were taken in strict compliance with local laws and regulations.","zh-CN":"*** 本页面所有视频和图片均在严格遵守当地相关法律法规的情况下拍摄。"},"v4.wm162.note4":{"en":"**** DJI Mini 3 Pro must be activated in the DJI Fly App before use.","zh-CN":"**** DJI Mini 3 Pro 须通过 DJI Fly app 激活后使用。"},"v4.wm162.note5":{"en":"1. Standard aircraft weight (including DJI Mini 3 Pro Intelligent Flight Battery, propellers, and a microSD card). The actual product weight may vary due to differences in batch materials and external factors. Registration is not required in some countries and regions. Check local rules and regulations before use.","zh-CN":"[1] 飞行器标准重量（含 DJI Mini 3 Pro 智能飞行电池、桨叶和 microSD 卡）。产品重量可能会因物料批次不同等原因而有所差异，请以实际产品为准；该产品在部分国家或地区免注册，请查询并确认当地法律法规。"},"v4.wm162.note6":{"en":"2. Measured at a constant speed of 21.6 kph in windless conditions. With DJI Mini 3 Pro Intelligent Flight Battery, the aircraft can fly for up to 34 mins. With the Intelligent Flight Battery Plus (sold separately and only in select countries), flight time is extended to up to 47 mins, but the aircraft will weigh more than 249 g.","zh-CN":"[2] 无风环境下，以 21.6 公里/小时匀速飞行时测得。DJI Mini 3 Pro 智能飞行电池最长续航时间为 34 分钟；若使用长续航智能飞行电池（该配件需单独购买），最长续航时间为 47 分钟，且机身重量会超过 249 克，请在飞行前查询、确认并严格遵守当地法律法规。"},"v4.wm162.note7":{"en":"3. HDR video does not support video recording at over 30fps.","zh-CN":"[3] 该功能不支持 30fps 以上帧率的录像规格。"},"v4.wm162.note8":{"en":"5. APAS 4.0 is not available while recording 4K/48fps, 4K/50fps, 4K/60fps, 2.7K/48fps, 2.7K/50fps, 2.7K/60fps, and 1080p/120fps video.","zh-CN":"[4] 录制 4K/48fps、4K/50fps、4K/60fps、2.7K/48fps、2.7K/50fps、2.7K/60fps、1080p/120fps 视频时，APAS 4.0 功能不可用。"},"v4.wm162.note9":{"en":"6. FCC compliant and with no obstructions in an outdoor open area.","zh-CN":"[5] FCC 标准，在室外空旷无干扰环境下测得。"},"v4.wm162.text1":{"en":"Fly Mini, Create Big","zh-CN":"小有成就"},"v4.wm162.text10":{"en":"Packed With Performance","zh-CN":"轻巧依旧，续航更“能打”"},"v4.wm162.text11":{"en":"Mini 3 Pro sports a completely new look that is optimized to get more out of every flight. With larger propellers, an aerodynamic body tilt, and a powerful obstacle sensing system, the streamlined design allows for increased flight time and safety. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe reimagined gimbal offers a wider rotation range for low-angle shots and True Vertical Shooting, allowing endless creative opportunities. Every aspect of this facelift has been carefully considered to take Mini to never-before-seen heights.","zh-CN":"全新产品构型设计通过改变机身倾角和增大桨叶面积，不仅降低了风阻，动力效能也大幅提升，令 DJI Mini 3 Pro 的续航得到显著突破；同时扩大了障碍物感知范围，实现灵活顺畅的避障效果；云台转动范围也得以拓宽，无损竖拍、大角度仰拍，都不在话下，赋予视觉创作更多可能性。"},"v4.wm162.text12":{"en":"Fold Up and Go","zh-CN":"轻松飞，放心拍"},"v4.wm162.text13":{"en":"For creators on the move, hassle-free use is key. Weighing less than 249 g, Mini 3 Pro doesn't require registration in most countries and regions. \u003csup\u003e[1]\u003c/sup\u003e The foldable and compact design also makes it easy to carry along with you on your next hike, beach day, or impromptu weekend away. Be ready to capture breathtaking footage when inspiration strikes.","zh-CN":"DJI Mini 3 Pro 超轻型机身采用可折叠设计，收纳便捷，可轻松放进口袋；重量低于 249 克\u003csup\u003e[1]\u003c/sup\u003e，在大部分国家/地区无需注册或培训即可快速起飞。带上它，说走就走，想拍就拍。"},"v4.wm162.text14":{"en":"Sweet Air Time","zh-CN":"秀出续航硬实力"},"v4.wm162.text15":{"en":"Capture and explore more of your surroundings with an extended flight time of up to 34 minutes. DJI Mini 3 Pro's Intelligent Flight Battery is ultra-lightweight and has enough power to cover your aerial photography needs.","zh-CN":"标配的 DJI Mini 3 Pro 智能飞行电池最长续航可达 34 分钟，足以完成大部分航拍场景拍摄，轻装上阵，轻享创作过程。"},"v4.wm162.text16":{"en":"If you're the kind of person that likes to push each flight to the limit, we've got you covered too. Upgrade to the Intelligent Flight Battery Plus and enjoy care-free exploration for up to 47 minutes. \u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"还有长续航智能飞行电池可供选择，让你飞足 47 分钟\u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e，拥有充裕的取景和构图空间，去探索广阔天地。告别电量焦虑，飞行更尽兴。"},"v4.wm162.text17":{"en":"You Shot That on Mini?!","zh-CN":"迷你身形，集结强大影像力"},"v4.wm162.text18":{"en":"Fly by Day","zh-CN":"全天候拍摄"},"v4.wm162.text19":{"en":"Fly by Night","zh-CN":"应对自如"},"v4.wm162.text2":{"en":"Under 249 g \u003csup\u003e[1]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"低于 249 克\u003csup\u003e[1]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text20":{"en":"Capture the subtlety of light and shadows as you head out on a day trip.\u003cbr\u003eShoot with clarity and less noise as evening falls.\u003cbr\u003eSavor the moment, stay true to your creative process, and trust Mini 3 Pro to capture your world.","zh-CN":"在日间，光与影更清晰。\u003cbr\u003e在黑夜，天与地更纯净。\u003cbr\u003e直出即大片，创作更随心。"},"v4.wm162.text21":{"en":"Pro","zh-CN":"影像系统"},"v4.wm162.text22":{"en":"And We Mean It","zh-CN":"真 Pro"},"v4.wm162.text23":{"en":"DJI Mini 3 Pro is outstanding in a wide range of lighting conditions, so you can always be ready to create. The 1/1.3-inch CMOS sensor features dual native ISO and supports the direct output of HDR footage. \u003csup\u003e[3]\u003c/sup\u003e Every image is enriched with a higher dynamic range to reveal more detail in highlights and shadows.","zh-CN":"在各种光线环境下 DJI Mini 3 Pro 都有出色的影像表现，激发无限灵感。1/1.3 英寸影像传感器拥有双原生 ISO，支持直出 HDR 影像\u003csup\u003e[3]\u003c/sup\u003e，更高的动态范围令明暗部位细节得以保留，提升画面层次感。"},"v4.wm162.text24":{"en":"Enjoy exceptional standards of aerial photography with bigger 2.4μm pixels \u003csup\u003e[4]\u003c/sup\u003e and an aperture ratio of f/1.7. With more light available, your images will appear true-to-life even in low-light scenes.","zh-CN":"f/1.7 大光圈配合感光能力惊人的 2.4μm 四合一大像素，带来纯净透亮的夜拍效果，细节充沛，画质细腻。动人的每一幕，尽数捕捉。"},"v4.wm162.text25":{"en":"Aerial Photography","zh-CN":"成像品质"},"v4.wm162.text26":{"en":"Done Right","zh-CN":"毫不逊色"},"v4.wm162.text27":{"en":"Take your content to the next level with stunning 4K HDR video \u003csup\u003e[3]\u003c/sup\u003e and 48MP RAW photos. Marvel at the rich clarity of every image, even as you zoom in. Or slow things down as the world gets hectic with dramatic 1080p/120fps slow-motion video.","zh-CN":"支持录制 4K HDR 视频\u003csup\u003e[3]\u003c/sup\u003e和拍摄 4800 万像素 RAW 格式照片，画面放大后，依然清晰细腻。同时支持 1080p/120fps 慢动作摄影，在快节奏的生活中慢下来，发掘另一种乐趣。"},"v4.wm162.text28":{"en":"4K HDR\u003cbr\u003eVideo","zh-CN":"4K HDR\u003cbr\u003e视频"},"v4.wm162.text29":{"en":"1080p/120fps\u003cbr\u003eVideo","zh-CN":"1080p/120fps\u003cbr\u003e慢动作视频"},"v4.wm162.text3":{"en":"Tri-Directional Obstacle Sensing","zh-CN":"三向环境感知"},"v4.wm162.text30":{"en":"4K/60fps\u003cbr\u003eVideo","zh-CN":"4K/60fps\u003cbr\u003e视频"},"v4.wm162.text31":{"en":"48MP\u003cbr\u003ePhoto","zh-CN":"4800 万像素\u003cbr\u003e照片"},"v4.wm162.text33":{"en":"Color Outside the Lines","zh-CN":"创意，任你发挥"},"v4.wm162.text34":{"en":"D-Cinelike Color mode provides more visual information, offering you richer color possibilities and more flexibility when editing.","zh-CN":"新增 D-Cinelike 色彩模式，能记录更丰富的色彩细节，过渡平滑自然，让热爱创作的你有更广阔的调整空间，尽情挥洒灵感。"},"v4.wm162.text35":{"en":"Peace of Mind as You Fly","zh-CN":"怎么飞，安全都是第一"},"v4.wm162.text36":{"en":"Fly with confidence as you navigate the skies. DJI Mini 3 Pro is fully upgraded to support active obstacle sensing and stable video transmission.","zh-CN":"DJI Mini 3 Pro 的避障和图传系统迎来全方位革新，可轻松实现灵活绕障和稳定的影像传输，各项安全性能组合发力，实力不容小觑。"},"v4.wm162.text37":{"en":"Tri-Directional Obstacle Sensing","zh-CN":"三向避障，多面探测"},"v4.wm162.text38":{"en":"DJI Mini 3 Pro is hands-down our safest Mini to date. Equipped with forward, backward, and downward dual-vision sensors and an all-new aircraft design, it offers a broader sensing range and enhanced safety.","zh-CN":"配备前视、后视、下视双目视觉感应系统和 ToF，同时得益于全新的机身设计，障碍物感应范围进一步增大，共同打造了 DJI Mini 系列迄今安全性最强的无人机。安全高标准，飞行少担忧。"},"v4.wm162.text39":{"en":"Did We Mention APAS 4.0?","zh-CN":"别忘了，还有 APAS 4.0"},"v4.wm162.text4":{"en":"4K HDR Video","zh-CN":"4K HDR 视频"},"v4.wm162.text40":{"en":"Advanced Pilot Assistance Systems (APAS 4.0) \u003csup\u003e[5]\u003c/sup\u003e detects objects in the aircraft's flight path in real-time. This allows DJI Mini 3 Pro to avoid obstacles, even in complicated environments.","zh-CN":"APAS 4.0（飞行辅助系统）\u003csup\u003e[4]\u003c/sup\u003e可实时探测飞行路径上的物体，即使身处复杂环境，DJI Mini 3 Pro 也能灵活躲避障碍物，飞行过程中安全守护不间断。"},"v4.wm162.text41":{"en":"Clear and Stable\u003cbr\u003eFrom City to Valley","zh-CN":"O3 图传“护体”，稳住大场面"},"v4.wm162.text42":{"en":"DJI Mini 3 Pro boasts a flagship-level video transmission system in DJI O3. \u003cbr\u003eIt ensures a 1080p/30fps live feed at distances of up to 12 km. \u003csup\u003e[6]\u003c/sup\u003e From city views to outdoor adventure, always fly with a crisp and reliable live feed.","zh-CN":"采用 DJI O3 旗舰型数字图传，1080p/30fps 最高实时图传画质和 12 公里\u003csup\u003e[5]\u003c/sup\u003e最远传输距离，一并奉上。无论是拍摄城市景观，还是在野外探索，都能飞得稳，看得清。"},"v4.wm162.text43":{"en":"Enjoy smooth flying and responsive control with the DJI RC-N1 Remote Controller or the new DJI RC. Both controllers offer a max video bitrate of 18 Mbps delivered at an ultra-low latency of 120 ms.","zh-CN":"无论是 RC-N1 遥控器还是全新带屏遥控器 DJI RC，均可通过 O3 图传实现 18Mbps 最大图传码率和 120 毫秒超低图传延时，操控反馈迅速，其流畅度与灵敏度，都超乎想象。"},"v4.wm162.text44":{"en":"Instantly Share-Worthy","zh-CN":"易拍，趣拍，分享快一拍"},"v4.wm162.text45":{"en":"Capture unforgettable content and instantly share your adventure on the go. DJI Mini 3 Pro offers an extensive range of intelligent features so you can add show-stopping moments and creative flair to any video.","zh-CN":"还有各项智能功能齐聚于 DJI Mini 3 Pro，带来丰富的视觉效果和多样玩法，让你不费吹灰之力拍大作，畅享航拍乐趣。"},"v4.wm162.text47":{"en":"True Vertical Shooting","zh-CN":"无损竖拍"},"v4.wm162.text48":{"en":"Let's try that again in portrait. Quickly switch between landscape and portrait in just a tap. The re-engineered camera gimbal rotates 90°, so you don't have to compromise on image quality. True Vertical Shooting gives you detailed shots, instantly ready for social media.","zh-CN":"采用全新云台构型设计，云台转动限位更小，支持无裁切竖拍，画质不妥协，引领竖版航拍视频\u003cspan style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"\u003e潮流。\u003c/span\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text49":{"en":"FocusTrack \u003csup\u003e[7]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"焦点跟随\u003csup\u003e[6]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text5":{"en":"Extended Battery Life \u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"可选 34/47 分钟\u003cspan style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"\u003e续航\u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e\u003c/span\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text50":{"en":"Find creative ways to follow your subject with FocusTrack. The suite includes ActiveTrack 4.0, Spotlight 2.0, and Point of Interest 3.0, three powerful storytelling tools.","zh-CN":"配备智能跟随、聚焦、兴趣点环绕三种跟拍模式，将主角始终锁定在 C 位。"},"v4.wm162.text51":{"en":"MasterShots","zh-CN":"大师镜头"},"v4.wm162.text52":{"en":"MasterShots is a true game-changer for any beginner aerial photographer. Simply select your subject, and Mini 3 Pro will execute a sequence of pro maneuvers, generating a short cinematic video afterward. There's a good reason why this is a fan favorite.","zh-CN":"一键启用后，飞行器自动拍摄多条具有专业运镜水准的短片，并完成剪辑和配乐，惬意之间，\u003cbr\u003e大片到手。"},"v4.wm162.text53":{"en":"Hyperlapse","zh-CN":"延时摄影"},"v4.wm162.text54":{"en":"Speed up time with just a few taps by creating a striking hyperlapse or timelapse video. Capture moving traffic or rolling clouds and inject some drama into your videos.","zh-CN":"轻点几下屏幕，只需静候片刻，时光流转，云卷云舒，都浓缩在高画质延时影片中。"},"v4.wm162.text55":{"en":"Digital Zoom","zh-CN":"数码变焦"},"v4.wm162.text56":{"en":"Get closer to your subject with 4x digital zoom. This lets you capture scenes without disturbing them and scout shots from afar.","zh-CN":"录制 1080p 解析度影片时，最高可选择 4 倍数码变焦，远近焦段随心切换，构图灵活自如，激发更多创作巧思。"},"v4.wm162.text57":{"en":"Panorama","zh-CN":"全景拍摄"},"v4.wm162.text58":{"en":"Capture the vastness of any landscape with Wide-angle, 180°, Vertical, \u003cbr\u003eand Sphere panorama shots.","zh-CN":"可拍摄 180°/广角/竖拍/球形全景照片，提供多样化视角，让你换个角度看世界。"},"v4.wm162.text58.added":{"en":"180°","zh-CN":"180°"},"v4.wm162.text58.added1":{"en":"Wide-angle","zh-CN":"超广角"},"v4.wm162.text58.added3":{"en":"Sphere","zh-CN":"球形"},"v4.wm162.text59":{"en":"QuickTransfer","zh-CN":"手机快传"},"v4.wm162.text6":{"en":"True Vertical Shooting","zh-CN":"无损竖拍"},"v4.wm162.text60":{"en":"Instantly ready to share your creations, Mini 3 Pro supports high-speed Wi-Fi downloads at up to 25 Mbps.","zh-CN":"支持 Wi-Fi 高速下载，最高速率可达 25MB/s，即拍即传，效率当先。"},"v4.wm162.text61":{"en":"Take Your Mini to the Max","zh-CN":"配件，航拍实力助攻"},"v4.wm162.text62":{"en":"Expand the way you create and fly with these practical accessories.","zh-CN":"将这些实用配件收入囊中，为影像创作加持。从容飞行，航拍时更能大显身手。"},"v4.wm162.text63":{"en":"DJI Mini 3 Pro Intelligent Flight Battery Plus \u003csup\u003e[8]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"DJI Mini 3 Pro 长续航智能飞行电池\u003csup\u003e[7]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text64":{"en":"With a 47-minute max flight time, \u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e the Intelligent Flight Battery Plus gives you more every time you take off.","zh-CN":"最长续航时间 47 分钟\u003csup\u003e[2]\u003c/sup\u003e，提供充裕的取景和构图空间，让你告别续航焦虑，尽兴飞行，满载而归。"},"v4.wm162.text65":{"en":"DJI RC \u003csup\u003e[9]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"DJI RC\u003csup\u003e[8]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text66":{"en":"Free up your phone with DJI RC. This lightweight remote controller features a built-in screen designed explicitly for DJI Mini 3 Pro. With the DJI Fly app pre-installed, you can focus on flying and save your phone's battery.","zh-CN":"专为 DJI Mini 3 Pro 打造的轻量化带屏遥控器，内置 DJI Fly app，操作便捷高效。航拍不会因手机来电等通知而中断，让你专注创作，享受飞行乐趣，也为手机节省更多电量。"},"v4.wm162.text67":{"en":"Two-Way Charging Hub \u003csup\u003e[8]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"双向充电管家\u003csup\u003e[7]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text68":{"en":"This practical charging accessory can hold and power three batteries in sequence. Take it with you to charge your remote controller, smartphone, or other devices when a top-up is needed.","zh-CN":"可同时为遥控器和三块电池依次充电，也可充当移动电源给遥控器或手机等设备充电，还能收纳电池，方便携带。"},"v4.wm162.text69":{"en":"ND Filters Set \u003csup\u003e[8]\u003c/sup\u003e","zh-CN":"ND 镜套装\u003csup\u003e[7]\u003c/sup\u003e"},"v4.wm162.text7":{"en":"FocusTrack","zh-CN":"焦点跟随"},"v4.wm162.text70":{"en":"Adapt to changing lighting conditions with ND16/64/256 filters and always be ready for the perfect shot.","zh-CN":"提供 ND16/64/256 减光滤镜套装，应对日间强光拍摄环境。"},"v4.wm162.text8":{"en":"Remarkably Mini","zh-CN":"小身形，也能成就大作"},"v4.wm162.text9":{"en":"The mini-sized, mega-capable DJI Mini 3 Pro is just as powerful as it is portable. Weighing less than 249 g and with upgraded safety features, it's not only regulation-friendly, it's also the safest in its series. \u003csup\u003e[1]\u003c/sup\u003e With a 1/1.3-inch sensor and top-tier features, it redefines what it means to fly Mini.","zh-CN":"延续 Mini 系列的轻巧便携，DJI Mini 3 Pro 搭载 1/1.3 英寸传感器，带来影像性能大跃升，不分昼夜，直出高品质画面；更将创新构型、智能功能、避障系统集于一身，全方位革新航拍体验。"},"v4.wm162.watchvideo":{"en":"Watch Video","zh-CN":"观看影片"},"view.common.search_dji":{"en":"Search dji.com...","zh-CN":"搜索 dji.com..."}},"editting":{}},"context":{"mobileMode":false,"originPath":"/cn/mini-3-pro","withPathProject":["enterprise","ag","auto"]},"editSetting":{"settings":{},"editData":{},"translation":{}},"editPageData":{"edittingId":null,"loadingState":"initial","error":null,"data":{}},"page":{"loadingState":"success","error":null,"data":{"url":"mini-3-pro","subdomain":"www","meta_title":"DJI Mini 3 Pro - 小有成就 - DJI 大疆创新","meta_description":"延续 Mini 系列的轻巧便携，DJI Mini 3 Pro 搭载 1/1.3 英寸传感器，带来影像性能大跃升，不分昼夜，直出高品质画面；更将创新构型、智能功能、避障系统集于一身，全方位革新航拍体验。 ","meta_keywords":null,"components_data":[{"slug":"productPage","data":{"id":27055,"component_data":null,"translation_data":null}},{"slug":"wm162Banner","data":{"id":27054,"component_data":{"downgrade":false,"screen1Bg":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/8bae0f9396120d35287dea329a202f78.jpg","screen1FightImage":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/7fa523af44740a43aa26a2d5abbcc8ea.png","screen1HandImage":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/fc4b664ced78d2aaa5ca0fb042f2c0c2.png","logoSvg":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/478a545f8d5181c6c7ec65212f450a75.svg","description":"v4.wm162.text1","iconList":[{"icon":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/d73b23783cb297e5d51cf5cbf1c85b68.svg","text":"v4.wm162.text2","_arrayItemId":"aab6"},{"icon":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/c2820f644cd96d0ecfaefab3034aefc6.svg","text":"v4.wm162.text3","_arrayItemId":"c650"},{"icon":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/01be55b282f9cc45534162f21af0da90.svg","text":"v4.wm162.text4","_arrayItemId":"ba1c"},{"icon":"https://dji-official-fe.djicdn.com/dps/1e943219572ffb626074a8f9fe473ca5.svg","text":"v4.wm162.text5","_arrayItemId":"fef0"},{"i